I’m so thankful to know that they will know what unconditional support and love feels like from their Dad. Thank you for all the school pick up’s and drop off’s, the hockey practices, the late night rollerblade runs around the neighborhood, and the dance parties. Thank you for all that you do to keep our little family thriving. We love you forever. ❤️

One of my favorite parts of what I do is the friends I collect along the way. I have known @candicehuffine for over ten years and she is one person I’m so lucky to know. We have been through diff relationships, diff hair looks, old clients, new clients, we survived long hours on set, she knew me before I had kiddos, she is a light and always the funniest person in the room. When she texted me to see if I knew anyone in Vegas who could do her hair I was like 🙋🏻‍♀️ me friend, I’m coming! How lucky I am to know you friend and I’m so happy I could spend a few hours with you on your beautiful day! Cheers to you and the perfect @shell_sparks 🥂❤️
